{
  "title": "Argentinian Cheese Curds Casserole",
  "description": "A tangy and savory casserole featuring cheese curds and score-fat, perfect for a sick day, with a low-glycemic friendly twist. This dish is a hearty and comforting Argentinian classic.",
  "cuisine": "Argentinian",
  "diet": [
